msgctxt "QL_HigakkareMini_RedDragon_Desc"
msgid ""
"You learned of a legend that says to offer a\n"
"<1.se_co>sacred relic<2.re_co> to the <3.se_co>Spring of Power<4.re_co>, "
"located\n"
"to the <5.se_co>west<6.re_co> of East Akkala Stable.\n"
"\n"
"The legend didn't say what this <7.se_co>sacred relic<8.re_co>\n"
"might be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_HigakkareMini_RedDragon_Finish"
msgid ""
"\"Offer Dinraal's scale received from the red spirit\n"
"to the Spring of Power.\"\n"
"\n"
"When you carried out the statue's suggestion\n"
"and dropped Dinraal's scale into the\n"
"Spring of Power, an ancient shrine\n"
"revealed itself.\n"
"\n"
"So the sacred relic was indeed Dinraal's scale..."
msgstr ""

